Description:
In the center of the sewers you find a throne and next to it a frozen ratman holding a goblet. Unlike the others, this ratman still seems to be alive and with a little magic you manage to unfreeze him. When he recovers he says to you:

"Where is the king, what happened? mmm... It seems that you have saved me, thank you very much.

I serve the king with a variety of goblets, some of which are even magical! I took them out of the vault and I stole others from the elves... hehehe...
DescriptionAction: As thanks for saving me, I'll sell you some of my goblets."
